snippet.title: Johnny Depp WINS Against Amber Heard In Defamation
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp WINS Against Amber Heard In Defamation

Join us in today’s video as we share with you Johnny Depp’s sentiments about how Amber Heard treated him! For several years now, Johnny Depp has been entangled in legal battles both directly and indirectly tied to his split from ex-wife Amber Heard. Their relationship was a tabloid magazine’s dream: Hollywood A-lister falls in love with up-and-coming ingenue on set. 

Depp lost his libel case against The Sun in U.K. court over the publication describing him as the attacker. You might well assume that Depp's career is in ruins and his reputation irretrievably damaged. But this isn’t the case in any way. Be sure to watch the whole video and see what really happened in the case of Johnny Depp against Amber Heard! In addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
